Definition: any of various thorny shrubs of the genus Pyracantha bearing small white flowers followed by hard red or orange-red berries
Synonyms: pyracanth, fire_thorn, firethorn, shrub, genus_Pyracantha, m, any, of, various, thorny, shrubs, the, genus, bearing, small, white, flowers, followed, by, hard, red, or, orange-red, berries
Category: noun.plant
